snippet.title: Arcade Game: Demolition Derby (1984 Midway)
snippet.description:
A Driving game where you drive your car in a demolition derby to hit and crash other cars. Collect tools such as wrench, screwdrivers, and car keys to earn bonus points.

Note: Used the no damage and fast recovery damage cheat. The game is endless.
